<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>١٩- إِنَّهُمْ أَلْفَوْا آباءَهُمْ ضالِّينَ <span class="c2">(٦٩)</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>فَهُمْ عَلى آثارِهِمْ يُهْرَعُونَ <span class="c2">(٧٠)</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>وَلَقَدْ ضَلَّ قَبْلَهُمْ أَكْثَرُ الْأَوَّلِينَ <span class="c2">(٧١)</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>وَلَقَدْ أَرْسَلْنا فِيهِمْ مُنْذِرِينَ <span class="c2">(٧٢)</span><a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>فَانْظُرْ كَيْفَ كانَ عاقِبَةُ الْمُنْذَرِينَ <span class="c2">(٧٣)</span><a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>إِلَّا عِبادَ اللَّهِ الْمُخْلَصِينَ <span class="c2">(٧٤)</span> <span class="c2">«١»</span><a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>٢٠- وَإِنَّ إِلْياسَ لَمِنَ الْمُرْسَلِينَ <span class="c2">(١٢٣)</span><a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>إِذْ قالَ لِقَوْمِهِ أَلا تَتَّقُونَ <span class="c2">(١٢٤)</span><a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>أَتَدْعُونَ بَعْلًا وَتَذَرُونَ أَحْسَنَ الْخالِقِينَ <span class="c2">(١٢٥)</span><a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>اللَّهَ رَبَّكُمْ وَرَبَّ آبائِكُمُ الْأَوَّلِينَ <span class="c2">(١٢٦)</span><a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>فَكَذَّبُوهُ فَإِنَّهُمْ لَمُحْضَرُونَ <span class="c2">(١٢٧)</span><a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>إِلَّا عِبادَ اللَّهِ الْمُخْلَصِينَ <span class="c2">(١٢٨)</span> <span class="c2">«٢»</span><a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>٢١- أَمْ لَكُمْ سُلْطانٌ مُبِينٌ <span class="c2">(١٥٦)</span><a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>فَأْتُوا بِكِتابِكُمْ إِنْ كُنْتُمْ صادِقِينَ<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span><span class="c2">(١٥٧)</span><a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>وَجَعَلُوا بَيْنَهُ وَبَيْنَ الْجِنَّةِ نَسَباً وَلَقَدْ عَلِمَتِ الْجِنَّةُ إِنَّهُمْ لَمُحْضَرُونَ <span class="c2">(١٥٨)</span><a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>سُبْحانَ اللَّهِ عَمَّا يَصِفُونَ <span class="c2">(١٥٩)</span><a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span>إِلَّا عِبادَ اللَّهِ الْمُخْلَصِينَ <span class="c2">(١٦٠)</span> <span class="c2">«٣»</span><a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span>٢٢- قالَ رَبِّ فَأَنْظِرْنِي إِلى يَوْمِ يُبْعَثُونَ <span class="c2">(٧٩)</span><a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span>قالَ فَإِنَّكَ مِنَ الْمُنْظَرِينَ <span class="c2">(٨٠)</span><a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p21"></span>إِلى يَوْمِ الْوَقْتِ الْمَعْلُومِ <span class="c2">(٨١)</span><a href="#p21" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p22"></span>قالَ فَبِعِزَّتِكَ لَأُغْوِيَنَّهُمْ أَجْمَعِينَ <span class="c2">(٨٢)</span><a href="#p22" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p23"></span>إِلَّا عِبادَكَ مِنْهُمُ الْمُخْلَصِينَ <span class="c2">(٨٣)</span> <span class="c2">«٤»</span><a href="#p23" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
