<p><span class="anchor" id="p25"></span>٢٣- قُلْ هُوَ اللَّهُ أَحَدٌ <span class="c2">(١)</span><a href="#p25" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
