<p><span class="anchor" id="p27"></span>لَمْ يَلِدْ وَلَمْ يُولَدْ <span class="c2">(٣)</span><a href="#p27" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p28"></span>وَلَمْ يَكُنْ لَهُ كُفُواً أَحَدٌ <span class="c2">(٤)</span> <span class="c2">«٥»</span><a href="#p28" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
